千万别 这底下可是沙虫的地盘
You wouldn't want to go down out there.  It's worm territory.

543
00:57:07,620 --> 00:57:08,530
沙尘云
Dust cloud.

544
00:57:09,920 --> 00:57:12,280
看到了
I see it.

545
