You can't know that.

649
01:09:17,840 --> 01:09:20,920
我自己也是刚刚知道 才怀上几周而已
I barely know that and it's only been few weeks.

650
01:10:01,480 --> 01:10:03,520
男爵找我们干什么?
What does the baron want with us?

651
01:10:03,680 --> 01:10:08,640
